➜黄鹤楼首次开放夜间行浸式体验
http://www.sohu.com/a/421338982_362042	3459
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200928/dca0f72c03074997b11049714d0df888.jpeg" /></p>
<p>游客夜游黄鹤楼。余倩 摄</p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200928/cf5786158106455bbfd7975ecf83a474.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200928/b6f4b588a4184440b58e1701766e9e75.jpeg" /></p>
<p>《夜上黄鹤楼》行浸式光影演艺体验版将于“十一”亮相。刘帅 摄</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
